WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.380 --> 00:00:04.270
Yaxshi, oxirgi mashg‘ulot savoli
aslida ikki qismdan iborat edi.

00:00:04.270 --> 00:00:08.880
Birinchi qism activity_main.xml 
kirib undagi kodni 

00:00:08.880 --> 00:00:13.770
brauzerda kodni o‘zgartirgan tarzda 
o‘zgartirishdan iborat edi.

00:00:13.770 --> 00:00:16.110
Keyingi qismi aslida ushbu yangi ilovani
telefoningizda ishga tushirishdan iborat edi.

00:00:16.110 --> 00:00:19.330
Shunday qilib, men oldinga qadam tashlab
birinchi qismini bajaraman.

00:00:19.330 --> 00:00:22.680
Men res jildi, so‘ng joylashuv 
tartibi jildiga o‘tib,

00:00:22.680 --> 00:00:25.463
uning ichida men activity_main.xml 
faylini ko‘raman.

00:00:25.463 --> 00:00:27.200
Uni ochish uchun ikki marta bosing.

00:00:28.330 --> 00:00:31.370
Xo‘p, men endi TextView 
farzand ko‘rinishini ko‘ryapman

00:00:31.370 --> 00:00:33.850
u RelativeLayout otasi 
ichida joylashgan.

00:00:33.850 --> 00:00:36.410
Endi bu TextView 
meni qiziqtiradi.

00:00:36.410 --> 00:00:38.944
Endi men o‘zimdan so‘rayman, nima qilishim kerak?

00:00:38.944 --> 00:00:42.150
 RelativeLayout ni, TextView ni 
yoki ikkalasini o‘zgartirishim kerak?

00:00:42.150 --> 00:00:44.605
Va javob men TextView ni 
o‘zgartirishim kerak.

00:00:45.920 --> 00:00:49.490
Yana bir savol, qaysi atribut yoki
atributlarni o‘zgartirishim kerakmi?

00:00:49.490 --> 00:00:51.874
Bunga javob - TextView ning

00:00:51.874 --> 00:00:54.430
 android:text atributi.

00:00:54.430 --> 00:00:55.410
Shuning uchun men bu erga boraman.

00:00:56.780 --> 00:01:01.720
Joriy qiymatni o‘chirib tashlamoqchiman,
(albatta, qo‘shtirnoqlarni qoldirgan holda) va

00:01:01.720 --> 00:01:06.270
 Happy Birthday Ben! deb yozaman

00:01:06.270 --> 00:01:07.198
Juda yaxshi.

00:01:07.198 --> 00:01:10.090
Shunday qilib, qilishim kerak bo‘lgan 
ishning men birinchi qismini qildim

00:01:10.090 --> 00:01:13.650
bu activity_main.xml faylini o‘zgartiradi.

00:01:13.650 --> 00:01:14.790
Endi buni telefonimga yozishim kerak.

00:01:14.790 --> 00:01:16.655
Va bu juda oddiy jarayon.

00:01:16.655 --> 00:01:19.515
Men bu yerda eng yuqori tomonga boraman va

00:01:19.515 --> 00:01:22.913
yashil tugmachani bosib
ilovani telefonimga o‘rnataman.

00:01:22.913 --> 00:01:26.785
Endi "Play" tugmasini bosing,
taxminan besh soniyada

00:01:26.785 --> 00:01:29.615
 Choose Device degan oyna qalqib chiqadi.

00:01:29.615 --> 00:01:31.365
Men hozirgina ko‘rsatganimdek
o‘z telefonimni tanlayman,

00:01:31.365 --> 00:01:34.215
va keyin OK tugmachasini bosaman.

00:01:34.215 --> 00:01:37.885
Va buni ko‘rish biroz qiyinroq, ammo
telefonimda endi Happy Birthday Ben paydo bo‘ldi.

